== Gentoo stand ==
Gentoo has a stand at FOSDEM 2017, following up [https://blog.sumptuouscapital.com/2016/01/gentoo-at-fosdem-2016/ last year's successful stand]. We are located at [https://fosdem.org/2017/schedule/buildings/#k K (level 1, group B) 2] between ReactOS/Haiku and CoreOS.

As last year we expect to announce a new livecd during FOSDEM 2017

