== Gentoo dinner ==

We'll meet (as every year) for the traditional Gentoo dinner on saturday evening. Since people were quite happy with the food, it'll most likely be at [http://www.woknroll.be/ Wok'n'Roll] again. That's a ~15min walk from the FOSDEM venue; we will meet and leave together after the Distributions devroom closes at 18:55, in front of the lecture hall K.4.601 of that devroom.

Please add yourself to one of the tables above if you want to join, so we can reserve a reasonable amount of places and tables! In case of organization questions, contact {{User|xaviermiller}}.

== Gentoo OpenPGP Web of Trust ==
Gentoo will not host a key signing party this year, but participants are encouraged to exchange and verify OpenPGP key data to build the Gentoo Web of Trust. Please bring printed information of the fingerprint and various UIDs you want certified along with a valid governmental ID matching the UID. You can use a service like [http://openpgp.quelltextlich.at/slip.html] to generate such a key slip.

